    <div>
      <p begin="00:00:18.617" end="00:00:22.200">Um, dois. Um, dois, tr&#234;s, quatro.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:22.278" end="00:00:23.520"/>
      <p begin="00:00:23.582" end="00:00:25.691">Se gosta da m&#250;sica de James Brown,</p>
      <p begin="00:00:25.691" end="00:00:27.585">esta noite vai passar um bom bocado.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:27.585" end="00:00:29.761">Esta noite estamos a celebrar o 62&#186; anivers&#225;rio</p>
      <p begin="00:00:29.761" end="00:00:33.850">de Black Velvet, James Brown Jr.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:33.850" end="00:00:35.906" region="top">Whoo, 62! </p>
      <p begin="00:00:36.476" end="00:00:38.526" region="top">Agora, comecem a bater palmas </p>
      <p begin="00:00:38.526" end="00:00:39.758" region="top">porque temos um jovem </p>
      <p begin="00:00:39.758" end="00:00:41.545" region="top">prestes a subir ao palco. </p>
      <p begin="00:00:41.545" end="00:00:43.690">Ele esteve no programa do David Letterman</p>
      <p begin="00:00:43.690" end="00:00:45.777">Batam palmas, conhe&#231;am e cumprimentem</p>
      <p begin="00:00:45.777" end="00:00:49.963">ao Black Velvet, James Brown, Jr.!</p>
      <p begin="00:00:49.963" end="00:00:52.279"/>
      <p begin="00:00:52.279" end="00:00:53.952"/>
      <p begin="00:00:53.952" end="00:00:59.249">&#9834; &#201; um mundo de homem. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:00:59.249" end="00:01:05.556">&#9834; Mas eu n&#227;o seria nada, nada... &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:01:05.556" end="00:01:06.715">- Imito o James Brown</p>
      <p begin="00:01:06.715" end="00:01:13.956">desde os meus 14 anos.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:13.956" end="00:01:16.475"/>
      <p begin="00:01:16.475" end="00:01:17.935"/>
      <p begin="00:01:17.935" end="00:01:21.271"/>
      <p begin="00:01:21.271" end="00:01:25.860"/>
      <p begin="00:01:25.860" end="00:01:29.767">Mas agora vou come&#231;ar a fazer de Charles Bradley.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:29.767" end="00:01:52.445"/>
      <p begin="00:01:52.599" end="00:01:54.471" region="top">O meu primeiro &#225;lbum de originais </p>
      <p begin="00:01:54.471" end="00:01:58.132" region="top">vai ficar &#224; venda em 25 de Janeiro. </p>
      <p begin="00:01:58.132" end="00:02:01.271">H&#225; 42 anos que luto</p>
      <p begin="00:02:01.271" end="00:02:03.014">para singrar na ind&#250;stria</p>
      <p begin="00:02:03.014" end="00:02:04.731">e, aos 62 anos,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:04.731" end="00:02:06.775">estou a come&#231;ar a encontrar o meu caminho.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:09.086" end="00:02:11.071">Nunca fiz dinheiro suficiente</p>
      <p begin="00:02:11.071" end="00:02:13.928">para me sustentar no mundo da m&#250;sica.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:13.928" end="00:02:15.993">,as espero que este &#225;lbum</p>
      <p begin="00:02:15.993" end="00:02:17.442">seja um ponto de viragem para mim,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:17.442" end="00:02:20.252">e que me possa sustentar atrav&#233;s da m&#250;sica.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:25.314" end="00:02:26.837">Hey, man.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:26.837" end="00:02:28.808">Vou buscar-te &#225;gua, ok?</p>
      <p begin="00:02:28.808" end="00:02:30.155">Hey, man.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:30.155" end="00:02:30.834">Este &#233; o meu p&#225;ssaro.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:30.834" end="00:02:32.647">Deixa-me louco.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:32.647" end="00:02:33.782">Fico zangado, saio da beira dele, vou para as traseiras, fecho a porta,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:33.782" end="00:02:35.520">Eu vou no quarto, fechar a porta,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:35.520" end="00:02:37.328">e deixo-o &#224; vontade para gritar quanto ele quiser.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:38.020" end="00:02:39.057">E ter a minha casinha est&#225;vel,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:39.057" end="00:02:40.590">n&#227;o &#233; tudo o que quero,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:40.590" end="00:02:43.199">mas gra&#231;as a Deus que tenho um telhado sobre a cabe&#231;a.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:44.221" end="00:02:45.529">Quando entro no meu apartamentozinho</p>
      <p begin="00:02:45.529" end="00:02:47.113">e fecho a minha porta,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:47.113" end="00:02:48.734">fico em paz.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:48.734" end="00:02:50.496">Mas quando entro nos bairros,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:50.496" end="00:02:53.225">quando entro no elevador,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:53.225" end="00:02:54.307">entrar l&#225;,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:54.307" end="00:02:55.545">&#233; a&#237; que come&#231;am os sarilhos.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:55.545" end="00:02:57.076">Nunca se sabe</p>
      <p begin="00:02:57.076" end="00:02:59.174">o que vai acontecer nessas noites.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:59.174" end="00:03:00.663">O tipo l&#225; de baixo,</p>
      <p begin="00:03:00.663" end="00:03:02.366">o nome dele &#233; Alfred,</p>
      <p begin="00:03:02.366" end="00:03:03.206">Tipo muito bom, n&#227;o chateia ningu&#233;m.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:03.206" end="00:03:04.783">&#201; um tipo religioso.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:04.783" end="00:03:06.731">Eles dispararam contra a casa dele.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:06.731" end="00:03:07.753">Ele mostrou-me todos os buracos</p>
      <p begin="00:03:07.753" end="00:03:08.478">onde foram disparados tiros.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:08.478" end="00:03:09.261">Eu disse: "Wow, man."</p>
      <p begin="00:03:09.261" end="00:03:10.741">Eu disse,</p>
      <p begin="00:03:10.741" end="00:03:13.017">N&#227;o era capaz de viver no r&#233;s-do-ch&#227;o.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:13.017" end="00:03:14.586">Quando as coisas ficam</p>
      <p begin="00:03:14.586" end="00:03:16.289">demasiado m&#225;s nos bairros,</p>
      <p begin="00:03:16.289" end="00:03:18.007">vou para casa da minha m&#227;e</p>
      <p begin="00:03:18.007" end="00:03:19.737">e durmo na cave dela.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:32.075" end="00:03:33.691">Ent&#227;o venho para aqui,</p>
      <p begin="00:03:33.691" end="00:03:36.011">e &#233; aqui que durmo.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:36.011" end="00:03:37.269">At&#233; ao dia seguinte,</p>
      <p begin="00:03:37.269" end="00:03:39.058">vou fazer os recados,</p>
      <p begin="00:03:39.058" end="00:03:40.105">cuidar de tudo o que precisamos</p>
      <p begin="00:03:40.105" end="00:03:43.638">para manter o telhado sobre ambas as nossas cabe&#231;as.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:43.931" end="00:03:47.370">Gosto de enrolar um pouco disto</p>
      <p begin="00:03:47.370" end="00:03:48.964">na forma de uma pequena bola.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:50.953" end="00:03:53.302">&#201; s&#243; meter estes l&#225; dentro.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:55.722" end="00:03:56.898">Hey, como est&#225; o arroz?</p>
      <p begin="00:03:57.067" end="00:03:58.366">- Deixa-me ver</p>
      <p begin="00:04:00.135" end="00:04:02.056">S&#243; mais um bocadinho.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:02.194" end="00:04:05.126">- Venho de uma fam&#237;lia de oito pessoas.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:05.188" end="00:04:08.021">O meu objectivo principal &#233; tomar conta</p>
      <p begin="00:04:08.021" end="00:04:11.799">da minha m&#227;e, e fazer o melhor que posso.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:12.707" end="00:04:14.664" region="top">- &#201; o meu menino, </p>
      <p begin="00:04:14.664" end="00:04:16.777" region="top">e adoro-o. </p>
      <p begin="00:04:16.883" end="00:04:18.556" region="top">Ele lava a minha roupa. </p>
      <p begin="00:04:18.726" end="00:04:19.466" region="top">Ele limpa a casa. </p>
      <p begin="00:04:19.466" end="00:04:20.945" region="top">No Dia dos Namorados, </p>
      <p begin="00:04:20.945" end="00:04:23.555" region="top">comprou-me uma caixa de chocolates. </p>
      <p begin="00:04:23.555" end="00:04:24.911" region="top">E o meu menino &#233; t&#227;o docinho </p>
      <p begin="00:04:24.911" end="00:04:26.138" region="top">quanto esses chocolates. </p>
      <p begin="00:04:26.138" end="00:04:27.835">Apenas fa&#231;o com que ela</p>
      <p begin="00:04:27.835" end="00:04:28.542">tenha uma vida calma,</p>
      <p begin="00:04:28.542" end="00:04:29.668">e</p>
      <p begin="00:04:29.668" end="00:04:31.712">ent&#227;o, ela n&#227;o tmr que se preocupar</p>
      <p begin="00:04:31.712" end="00:04:33.312">com contas nem nada.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:33.312" end="00:04:34.478">Assumi esse fardo,</p>
      <p begin="00:04:34.478" end="00:04:36.190">e n&#227;o sabia mesmo</p>
      <p begin="00:04:36.190" end="00:04:37.231">em que me estava a meter.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:37.231" end="00:04:38.493">Mas agora, j&#225; me comprometi.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:38.493" end="00:04:40.083">N&#227;o vou mudar.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:40.083" end="00:04:41.252">Ent&#227;o a &#250;nica coisa que posso &#233; tentar</p>
      <p begin="00:04:41.252" end="00:04:42.968">fazer com que algo funcione</p>
      <p begin="00:04:42.968" end="00:04:44.297">onde possa arranjar um rendimento decente</p>
      <p begin="00:04:44.297" end="00:04:47.211">para que eu possa viver e deixar viver.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:47.211" end="00:04:50.030">E isso &#233; tudo o que posso pedir da vida agora.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:50.138" end="00:04:56.875"/>
      <p begin="00:04:56.875" end="00:05:00.615">&#9834; And&#225;mos &#224;s voltas outra vez.&#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:00.615" end="00:05:05.222">&#9834; Onde p&#225;ra, ningu&#233;m sabe. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:05.222" end="00:05:08.565">&#9834; &#201; um frio, frio mundo. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:08.965" end="00:05:12.469">&#9834; &#201; um frio, frio mundo. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:14.254" end="00:05:16.173">&#9834; Como podemos parar as mudan&#231;as &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:16.173" end="00:05:21.219">&#9834; que decorrem na Am&#233;rica hoje? &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:31.033" end="00:05:35.022">&#9834; Ohhh, ohhh, ohhh &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:41.466" end="00:05:43.575">&#9834; Regressar. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:43.575" end="00:05:47.287">&#9834; Regressar &#224; Regra Dourada. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:47.287" end="00:05:48.994">&#9834; Oh. Ah. Uh. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:49.455" end="00:05:50.963">&#9834; Regressar &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:50.963" end="00:05:55.504">&#9834; Regressar &#224; Regra Dourada. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:55.504" end="00:05:58.215">&#9834; Bring it all down. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:58.215" end="00:06:11.844"/>
      <p begin="00:06:11.844" end="00:06:13.438">- Esta &#233; uma m&#250;sica</p>
      <p begin="00:06:13.438" end="00:06:15.399">do novo &#225;lbum, No Time for Dreaming.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:15.399" end="00:06:16.525">Charles Bradley</p>
      <p begin="00:06:16.525" end="00:06:17.652">e a Menahan Street Band.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:17.652" end="00:06:19.111">N&#227;o consigo acreditar</p>
      <p begin="00:06:19.111" end="00:06:20.445">que tenhas aparecido do nada,</p>
      <p begin="00:06:20.445" end="00:06:22.656">virtualmente desconhecido para n&#243;s.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:22.656" end="00:06:24.858">J&#225; gravou alguma vez antes?</p>
      <p begin="00:06:24.981" end="00:06:26.277">- N&#227;o.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:26.277" end="00:06:28.820">&#201; a primeira vez em que realmente come&#231;o a aparecer.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:28.820" end="00:06:30.349">- Sei que tem actuado.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:30.349" end="00:06:31.431">- Sim.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:31.431" end="00:06:32.420">- Como Black Velvet</p>
      <p begin="00:06:32.420" end="00:06:34.044">- Sim.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:34.044" end="00:06:35.335">- Ent&#227;o agora est&#225; a actuar como-</p>
      <p begin="00:06:35.335" end="00:06:37.064">como Charles Bradley?</p>
      <p begin="00:06:37.064" end="00:06:38.076">- Sim, sim.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:38.076" end="00:06:39.298">- Bem, tem uma &#243;ptima banda</p>
      <p begin="00:06:39.298" end="00:06:40.129">a apoi&#225;-lo.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:40.129" end="00:06:41.667">E, claro,</p>
      <p begin="00:06:41.667" end="00:06:43.302">com as pessoas da Daptone,</p>
      <p begin="00:06:43.302" end="00:06:44.463">sabe,</p>
      <p begin="00:06:44.463" end="00:06:45.287">que equipa maravilhosa que eles s&#227;o.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:45.287" end="00:06:46.597">E j&#225; viu es.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:46.597" end="00:06:49.276">o que aconteceu com a Sharon Jones, que, - Sim, sim.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:49.276" end="00:06:51.340">que, sabe, como voc&#234;,</p>
      <p begin="00:06:51.340" end="00:06:52.882">foi da completa obscuridade at&#233;,</p>
      <p begin="00:06:52.897" end="00:06:55.464">quem sabe as alturas a que voc&#234;s poder&#227;o subir.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:55.464" end="00:06:56.872">Ent&#227;o, este,</p>
      <p begin="00:06:56.872" end="00:06:59.067">deve ser um momento excitante para si?</p>
      <p begin="00:06:59.067" end="00:07:01.820">- Penso que Deus respondeu &#224;s minhas preces,</p>
      <p begin="00:07:01.820" end="00:07:03.864">sabe,</p>
      <p begin="00:07:03.864" end="00:07:06.033">perguntei-me a mim pr&#243;prio porque demorou tanto,</p>
      <p begin="00:07:06.033" end="00:07:07.451">mas n&#227;o podemos questionar Deus</p>
      <p begin="00:07:07.451" end="00:07:09.411">quando ele quer fazer coisas.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:09.411" end="00:07:12.348">Ent&#227;o, j&#225; eu com a minha idade avan&#231;ada, come&#231;ou a vir.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:12.348" end="00:07:13.916">- O que se segue?</p>
      <p begin="00:07:13.916" end="00:07:15.375">Quero dizer, est&#225; a pensar em grande?</p>
      <p begin="00:07:15.375" end="00:07:17.144">- Penso que o limite &#233; o c&#233;u.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:17.144" end="00:07:19.421">- Parab&#233;ns por este fant&#225;stico &#225;lbum.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:19.421" end="00:07:20.737">Independentemente do que aconte&#231;a com ele,</p>
      <p begin="00:07:20.737" end="00:07:22.632">&#233; um trabalho fant&#225;stico.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:22.632" end="00:07:24.943">Charleys Bradley na WFUV.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:25.113" end="00:07:28.346"/>
      <p begin="00:07:28.346" end="00:07:33.685">&#9834; Este mundo est&#225; a arder. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:33.685" end="00:07:39.107">&#9834; E ningu&#233;m quer assumir a culpa. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:39.107" end="00:07:44.286">&#9834; N&#227;o me digam como viver a minha vida. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:44.286" end="00:07:49.746">&#9834; Quando nunca sentiram a dor. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:49.746" end="00:07:55.790">&#9834; Ohhh. Ahhh. Ohhh &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:55.790" end="00:07:58.335">&#9834;Ohhh.&#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:58.335" end="00:08:01.051">&#9834; N&#227;o me v&#234;em chorar? &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:01.051" end="00:08:02.883" region="top">&#9834; Ohhh... &#9834; </p>
      <p begin="00:08:02.883" end="00:08:04.800"/>
      <p begin="00:08:04.800" end="00:08:06.051" region="top">- N&#227;o sei quantos artistas </p>
      <p begin="00:08:06.051" end="00:08:07.718" region="top">chegaram aos 62 anos de idade </p>
      <p begin="00:08:07.718" end="00:08:09.445" region="top">e lan&#231;aram o seu &#225;lbum de estreia. </p>
      <p begin="00:08:10.213" end="00:08:11.950" region="top">Ele poder&#225; ser o primeiro. </p>
      <p begin="00:08:12.777" end="00:08:14.936" region="top">- Este tipo, ele est&#225; a p&#244;r </p>
      <p begin="00:08:14.936" end="00:08:16.937" region="top">a p&#244;r as coisas em andamento. </p>
      <p begin="00:08:16.937" end="00:08:19.215" region="top">Ele trabalhou muito arduamente, durante muito tempo. </p>
      <p begin="00:08:19.338" end="00:08:20.858" region="top">E espero que </p>
      <p begin="00:08:20.858" end="00:08:21.734" region="top">pessoas suficientes o ou&#231;am a cantar, </p>
      <p begin="00:08:21.734" end="00:08:23.151">para que-</p>
      <p begin="00:08:23.151" end="00:08:24.361">que ele possa ter a vida</p>
      <p begin="00:08:24.361" end="00:08:26.139">que quer e tomar conta da sua fam&#237;lia.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:26.139" end="00:08:27.626"/>
      <p begin="00:08:27.626" end="00:08:30.701">&#9834; Uh. Yeah. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:30.701" end="00:08:33.120">&#9834; Estou a falar contigo rapariga. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:33.120" end="00:08:34.538">&#9834; Yeah. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:34.538" end="00:08:36.642">&#9834; Apenas tu ... &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:36.642" end="00:08:38.333">Fui at&#233; ao Gabe</p>
      <p begin="00:08:38.333" end="00:08:40.502">porque achei que ele sabia o que estava a fazer.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:40.502" end="00:08:42.129">Senti que ele me podia dar uma ajuda,</p>
