      <p begin="01:10:25.367" end="01:10:26.862">- Agrade&#231;o-te.</p>
      <p begin="01:10:26.986" end="01:10:52.255"/>
      <p begin="01:10:52.394" end="01:10:54.959">-Ele est&#225; realmente a apanhar os detalhes todos.</p>
      <p begin="01:10:55.082" end="01:11:04.246"/>
      <p begin="01:11:04.246" end="01:11:07.062">Ahh!</p>
      <p begin="01:11:07.062" end="01:11:08.836">&#201; assim que sou.</p>
      <p begin="01:11:21.449" end="01:11:24.273">Woo.</p>
      <p begin="01:11:24.725" end="01:11:58.065"/>
      <p begin="01:11:58.065" end="01:12:00.084">-Porque quando eu deixar este mundo, este mundo n&#227;o me deve nada.</p>
      <p begin="01:12:00.223" end="01:12:01.745">-Devolve-me o meu d&#243;lar agora.</p>
      <p begin="01:12:04.392" end="01:12:05.962">-Sai de cima de mim.</p>
      <p begin="01:12:06.089" end="01:12:07.791">-Man, devolve-me o meu d&#243;lar.</p>
      <p begin="01:12:08.810" end="01:12:17.605"/>
      <p begin="01:12:17.605" end="01:12:18.666">-Oh, o meu passaporte, aguarde um minuto.</p>
      <p begin="01:12:18.804" end="01:12:39.516"/>
      <p begin="01:12:39.655" end="01:12:41.596">-Poupa a tua lagosta.</p>
      <p begin="01:12:43.227" end="01:12:46.111">-Jimmy, tu n&#227;o comes lagosta, d&#225;s-me sempre a mim.</p>
      <p begin="01:12:46.280" end="01:12:47.576">-Hoje vou come&#231;ar a com&#234;-la</p>
      <p begin="01:12:47.791" end="01:13:09.549"/>
      <p begin="01:13:09.796" end="01:13:13.704">-Disseste bem r&#225;pido que a moeda era tua. Eu vi-a.</p>
      <p begin="01:13:13.811" end="01:13:14.871">-Apanhei-a.</p>
      <p begin="01:13:15.025" end="01:14:07.858"/>
    </div>
